OL,3,C14 year-old girl found dead in park
OL,4,Csuffered multiple stab wounds, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA 14-year-old girl found dead in a
OL,8,Fpark is believed to have died from
OL,9,Fmultiple stab wounds, an inquest
OL,10,Fopening has heard.
OL,12,FLilly Anne Jones was found dead in the
OL,13,FDuffryn Park area of Blaina on June 22
OL,14,Fafter being reported missing two days
OL,15,Fearlier.
OL,17,FAn inquest opening at Gwent Coroner's
OL,18,FCourt on Monday heard the 14 year-old
OL,19,Fwas found with injuries to her chest
OL,20,Fand neck.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
