PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783676987
OL,3,C14 year-old girl found dead in park
OL,4,Csuffered multiple stab wounds, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA 14 year-old boy, who cannot be named
OL,8,Ffor legal reasons, appeared at Cardiff
OL,9,FCrown Court last month accused of
OL,10,Fmurdering Lilly.
OL,12,FGwent Coroner's Court heard Lilly,
OL,13,Ffrom Blaina, was reported missing from
OL,14,Fher home address on the evening of
OL,15,FJune 20.
OL,17,FShe was discovered shortly after 10pm
OL,18,Fon June 22 in a woodland location near
OL,19,Fthe bowls club with injuries to her
OL,20,Fchest and neck.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783676987
OL,3,C14 year-old girl found dead in park
OL,4,Csuffered multiple stab wounds, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FSenior coroner Caroline Saunders said
OL,8,Fa post-mortem examination was
OL,9,Fconducted by Dr Richard Jones and
OL,10,Fprovided a provisional cause of death.
OL,12,FShe said: "The medical cause of death
OL,13,Fhe has provided me with is 1A,
OL,14,Fmultiple stab wounds to the neck and
OL,15,Ftrunk.
OL,17,F"The matter will be adjourned so that
OL,18,Ffurther inquiries can be made."
OL,20,FThe coroner set a provisional inquest
OL,21,Fdate of April 6 2027.
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
