PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783676987
OL,3,C14 year-old girl found dead in park
OL,4,Csuffered multiple stab wounds, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FLilly was last seen in High Street,
OL,8,FBlaina, at around 6.50pm on June 20.
OL,10,FParts of Pilgrims Park, which is
OL,11,Fadjacent to the A467 in Blaina, were
OL,12,Fcordoned off after her body was
OL,13,Fdiscovered.
OL,15,FFloral tributes were left close to the
OL,16,Fscene by members of the public.
OL,18,FA 14-year-old boy charged with her
OL,19,Fmurder appeared at court on June 29.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
