PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1783676987
OL,3,C14 year-old girl found dead in park
OL,4,Csuffered multiple stab wounds, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,8,FRecorder of Cardiff, fixed a trial
OL,9,Fdate beginning on November 23, which
OL,10,Fis due to last four weeks.
OL,12,FThe youth, who did not enter a plea to
OL,13,Fthe murder charge, was remanded into
OL,14,Fcustody until his next court
OL,15,Fappearance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
